Reasoning: The paper discusses the use of mobile devices equipped with cameras and IMUs for AR and robotics applications, which are relevant to computer vision (cs.CV) and robotics (cs.RO) sub-categories. The paper also mentions the use of commercial AR toolkits and public benchmark datasets, which are related to multimedia (cs.MM) and graphics (cs.GR) sub-categories. Additionally, the paper discusses the design of a logger to access raw data from AR sensors on mobile devices, which could be relevant to human-computer interaction (cs.HC) sub-category.
